overview: Molly and Jade have been very naughty. Their stepdads, pretending to be the girls boyfriends, trick them into blindfolding themselves and getting naked. Now the real fun begins! Maya and Blair bet on the Olympics with their stepdads. If the girls win they get new cars but if the dads win they get to fuck the girls! Lucky for the dads, they bet on the USA & win!
tagline: You get to fuck his daughter . . . but he gets to fuck yours!
title: Daughter Swap 4
